IT_DELV_SCHED_XMSN,VALUT_OF_SPL_STK,REBT_BASIS_1,INFLT_INDX_DTTM,NM_OF_REQSNR1,TIME_ZN_OF_RCPNT_LOC1,MRP_AREA,DOC_ITM,WRK_BRKDWN_STRC_ELMNT1,REQ_URGNCY,REQ_PRIR,CRM_SLS_ORDR_ITM_NUM,CUM_GOODS_RECIPT,NUM_OF_SER_NUM,EXTRNL_SRT_NUM,RETN_IN_PCT,DOWN_PMT_PCT,DOWN_PMT_AMT_IN_DOC_CRNCY,DOWN_PMT_DUE_DTTM,CENT_CNTRC_ITM_NUM,INCO_LOC_1_PLACE_OF_DEST,INCO_LOC_2_PLACE_OF_DELV,INCO_DEVT_PLACE_OF_DEST,STAT_VAL_FOR_FRGN_TRD,PROD_TYPE_GRP,ITM_NUM_FOR_RQST_FOR_QUTN,TRGT_VAL_AT_ITM_LVL_IN_PRCM,EXPTD_VAL_OF_OVRL_LMT,OVRL_LMT,WKA_WRK_PER_STRT_DTTM,WKA_WRK_PER_END_DTTM,WKA_PCT_OF_WG,WRK_TIME_IN_HRS,DATA_FIL_VAL_FOR_DATA_AGE,CMT_QTY,HI_LVL_ITM_IN_PRTL_QTY_REJ,ANNXNG_PKG_KEY,EXTD_KEY_FOR_ANNXNG_PKG,BASE_DTTM,ANNXNG_DT_TYPE,ANNXNG_STRT_DTTM,DEVT_PCT,QUTN_ITM_NUM,DELV_PRIR,SLS_DOC_ITM,VEND_CNFRM_TYPE,DOC_DTTM,ARUN_ORDR_PRIR,WRK_BRKDWN_STRC_ELMNT2,RSN_FOR_ORD (select *, ROW_NUMBER() over (partition by SRC_SYS_CD,PO_NUM,PO_LINE_NBR,CO_CD,PO_TYPE_CD,ORDER_SUF
 order by PO_NUM) as RNK FROM
(SELECT
  '{Config.sourceSystem}'  AS SRC_SYS_CD,
  f4311.pddoco AS PO_NUM,
  f4311.pdlnid AS PO_LINE_NBR,
  f4311.pdkcoo AS CO_CD,
  f4311.pddcto AS PO_TYPE_CD,
  NULL AS DEL_IND,
  TRIM(f4311.pdlitm) AS MATL_NUM,
  TRIM(f4311.pdmcu) AS PLNT_CD,
  TRIM(f4311.pdlocn) AS SLOC_CD,
  TRIM(f4311.pdvr01) AS INTRNL_REF_NUM,
  CAST(TRIM(f4311.pduorg) AS DECIMAL(18, 4)) AS PO_LINE_QTY,
  TRIM(f4311.pduom) AS PO_UOM_CD,
  NULL AS STK_TYPE_CD,
  NULL AS DELV_CMPLT_IND,
  TRIM(f4311.pdlnty) AS LINE_ITEM_TYPE_CD,
  NULL AS ACCT_ASGNMT_CAT_CD,
  NULL AS PRIN_PRCH_AGMT_NUM,
  NULL AS PRIN_PRCH_AGMT_LINE_NUM,
  TRIM(f4311.pdan8) AS DELV_ADDR_NUM,
  CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(18, 4)) AS GR_LEAD_TIME_DAYS_QTY,
  NULL AS SPL_STK_IND,
  NULL AS CNFRM_CD,
  NULL AS SUBCNTRC_IND,
  NULL AS PR_NUM,
  NULL AS PR_LINE_NBR,
  NULL AS BRAZILIAN_NCM_CD,
  NULL AS OUTB_DELV_CMPLT_IND,
  NULL AS ISU_SLOC_CD,
  TRIM(f4311.pdshan) AS CUST_NUM,
  TRIM(f4311.pdmcu) AS SHIPPING_PT_NUM,
  NULL AS EM_MATERIAL_CODE,
  NULL AS BASE_UOM,
  TRIM(f4311.pduom) AS PO_PRICE_UOM,
  CAST(TRIM(f4311.pdprrc) AS DECIMAL(18, 2)) AS PO_LINE_PRICE,
  CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(18, 2)) AS DOCUMENT_CURRENCY_GROSS_AMOUNT,
  CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(18, 2)) AS DOCUMENT_CURRENCY_NET_AMOUNT,
  CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(18, 4)) AS NUMRTR_FOR_CONV_ORDR_UNIT,
  CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(18, 4)) AS DENOM_FOR_CONV_ORDR_UNIT,
  CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(18, 4)) AS PRICE_UNIT,
  f4311.pdsfxo AS ORDER_SUF,
  CASE WHEN LOWER(TRIM(f4311.pdtrdj)) = 'null' OR TRIM(f4311.pdtrdj) = '' OR TRIM(f4311.pdtrdj) = '0' THEN NULL 
  ELSE to_timestamp(substr(CAST(date_add(concat(substr(CAST(CAST(TRIM(f4311.pdtrdj) AS INT) + 1900000 AS STRING),1,4),'-01-01'), CAST(substr(CAST(CAST(TRIM(f4311.pdtrdj) AS INT) + 1900000 AS string),5) AS INT )-1) AS STRING), 1, 10),'yyyy-MM-dd')
  END AS PO_LINE_DTTM,
  TRIM(f4311.pdpqor) as PRMRY_QTY_ORD,
  NULL as G_L_ACCT_NUM,
  NULL as PRCHSNG_DOC_CRT_DTTM,
  NULL as TAX_RPTG_CTRY_RGN,
  NULL as TAX_ON_SLS,
CAST(TRIM(f4311.pdurec) AS DECIMAL(18,4)) as STK_TFR_RECV_QTY,
NULL AS CONCAT_OF_EBELN_AND_EBELP,                    
NULL AS ORIG_OF_PRCHSNG_DOC_ITM,
NULL AS PRCHSNG_DOC_ITM_CHG_DTTM,
NULL AS SHRT_TEXT,

NULL AS MATL_GRP,

NULL AS TRGT_QTY,
NULL AS NUMRTR_CONV_ORDR_PRC_UNIT,
NULL AS DENOM_CONV_ORDR_PRC_UNIT,

NULL AS NUM_OF_DAYS_FST_REMNDR,
NULL AS NUM_OF_DAYS_SEC_REMNDR,                     
NULL AS NUM_OF_DAYS_THIRD_RMNDR,

NULL AS SHIPPING_INSTR,
NULL AS TRGT_VAL_FOR_OUTLINE_AGMT,
NULL AS NDEDT_INP_TAX,
NULL AS STD_RLSE_ORDR_QTY,
NULL AS PRC_DTRMN_DTTM,
NULL AS PRCHSNG_DOC_CAT,
NULL AS EFF_VAL_OF_ITM,
NULL AS ITM_AFFCT_CMMT,
NULL AS COND_GRP_WTH_SUP,
NULL AS ITM_DONT_QUAL_FOR_CASH_DISC,
NULL AS UPDT_GRP_FOR_STATS_UPDT,
NULL AS NET_WT,
NULL AS UNIT_OF_WT,
NULL AS TAX_JURIS,
NULL AS PRT_RLVNT_SCHED_LIN_EXIST,
NULL AS SETLM_RESV_NUM,
NULL AS ITM_NUM_OF_THE_SETLM_RESV,
NULL AS QUAL_INSP_IN_CNNOT_BE_CHG,
NULL AS CNTL_KEY_FOR_QUAL_MGMT,
NULL AS INTNL_ARTCL_NUM,
NULL AS PRFT_CTR,
NULL AS GRS_WT,
NULL AS VOL,
NULL AS VOL_UNIT,
NULL AS PKG_NUM,
NULL AS CUR_NOT_USED,

NULL AS LTST_POSBL_GOODS_RCPT,
NULL AS CNFG,
NULL AS EVAL_RCPT_SETLM,
NULL AS GR_BAS_SETLM_STRT_DTTM,
NULL AS LAST_XMSN,
NULL AS SEQ_NUM,
NULL AS ALLC_TBL_ITM,
NULL AS NUM_OF_PT,
NULL AS MATL_LDGR_ACT_AT_MATL_LVL,
NULL AS MIN_RMN_SHLF_LIF,
NULL AS ITM_NUM_OF_RFQ,
NULL AS MATL_TYPE,
NULL AS SBTOT_1_FROM_PRC_PCDR,                       
NULL AS SBTOT_2_FROM_PRC_PCDR,                       
NULL AS SBTOT_3_FROM_PRC_PCDR,                       
NULL AS SBTOT_4_FROM_PRC_PCDR,                       
NULL AS SBTOT_5_FROM_PRC_PCDR,                       
NULL AS SBTOT_6_FROM_PRC_PCDR,

  {Config.sourceDatabase}.f4311

  f4311._deleted_ = 'F'))
